U.K. Ministers to Delay News Corp., BSkyB Deal Ruling, Mail Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-06T22:49:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/u-k-ministers-to-delay-news-corp-bskyb-deal-ruling-mail-says.html
The U.K. government’s decision on
whether to approve  News Corp. (NWSA) ’s proposed takeover of  British Sky
Broadcasting Group Plc (BSY)  will be delayed until the Autumn amid
phone hacking allegations at its News of the World newspaper,
the Daily Mail reported, citing unnamed government sources.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
